# GitHub Workflow

- Remote repository: https://github.com/CodeMaestroPro/cyra-tech-platform
- GitHub account: CodeMaestroPro
- After completing module work, always:
  1. Stage relevant changes
  2. Create a descriptive commit message
  3. Push to GitHub (`git push origin main`)
- Do not leave completed work uncommitted or unpushed unless the user explicitly asks to hold changes.
- Use the module commit message format when applicable, e.g. `feat(module-01): ...`
